            <lg xml:id="TK132">
<l>parintōmpik kākka voḻukkan terintōmpit</l>
<l>tēriṉu maḵtē tuṇai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Guard propriety with utmost pains; though you may look hard</l>
<l>and scrutinize it, it is your friend.</l>
